metadata.name: KERMIT THE FROG: THROUGH THE AGES
metadata.description:
A blue chip collage consisting of 36 timeless DALL-E 2  imaginings of Kermit The Frog depicted in various visually iconic pieces of media.

These generations were originally exhibited by HeavensLastAngel in a legendary viral Twitter thread, and became a go-to reference often used to convey the paradigm-shifting power of OpenAI's DALL-E 2 image generator. 

This historic 1/1 NFT is a testament to the incredible technological advances that mankind has made in the 21st century, and will serve as a generational milestone as we continue to reach new heights. 

Original Twitter thread with listed media references: 

https://twitter.com/HvnsLstAngel/status/1531506455714492416
